From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Tue, 11 Mar 2025 14:36:24 -0700
Subject: perf build: Rename TEST_LOGS to SHELL_TEST_LOGS
Git-commit: ef238109a3d20a2af474bf758c50072a09591f19
Patch-mainline: v6.15-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Rename TEST_LOGS to SHELL_TEST_LOGS as later changes will add more
kinds of test logs.
Minor comment tweak in Makefile.perf as more than just test shell
tests are checked.

Reviewed-by: James Clark <james.clark@linaro.org>
